data.title: Aaron Ramsey stats and ratings
data.meta_description: Aaron Ramsey profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
Aaron Ramsey is 21 years old (Jan 21, 2003), 180 cm tall and plays for Burnley.

Aaron Ramsey prefers to play with right foot. His jersey number is 21.

Aaron Ramsey career statistics, match ratings, heatmap and goals are available on Sofascore for current and previous seasons. Last player match was Burnley - Arsenal (0 - 5) and Aaron Ramsey received 6.1 Sofascore rating.

If Aaron Ramsey is going to be in Burnley lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Aaron Ramsey plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Aaron Ramsey football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Aaron Ramsey played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
